        |          WHERE         |           HAVING            |
Tujuan  |    Memfilter baris     |  memfilter hasil aggregasi  |
Data    |    untuk semua data    |    untuk data aggregasi     |
        | Sebelum Grouping data  |    setelah grouping data    |
        |          WHERE         |           HAVING            |
        |          WHERE         |           HAVING            |

  # Contoh penggunaan bersama
    SELECT store, month, SUM(total_sales) as total_sales
    FROM sales
    WHERE city IN ("Jakarta", "Bekasi", "Depok" )
    GROUP BY store, month
    HAVING SUM(total_store) > 25000000
